{"tid":2098126,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大狀：裁決證明交通警造成車禍","createTime":"2020-07-07T09:07:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T10:16:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e3539d9f6c114c8187b0520bf50c9f24377d93ae","tid":2098126,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T09:07:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200707/WMJRO5M3U3ZJAMF4R4HUH7ZRVI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200707%2FWMJRO5M3U3ZJAMF4R4HUH7ZRVI%2F&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivZsm%2Bn8Fwo%2F6aJUx9arcu0Q%3D&h=e0e4353b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200707%2FWMJRO5M3U3ZJAMF4R4HUH7ZRVI%2F&h=d7271658\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200707/WMJRO5M3U3ZJAMF4R4HUH7ZRVI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n大狀：裁決證明交通警造成車禍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/txBNAyXqYMNMMxWLZgofMr8RMZ4=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IFB6DUKBBCMBN6XKOPBHHDJ3LE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FtxBNAyXqYMNMMxWLZgofMr8RMZ4%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIFB6DUKBBCMBN6XKOPBHHDJ3LE.jpg&h=5cb87f6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陸偉雄<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】死因庭昨裁定「死於意外」，同時指交通警導致車禍發生。<br />\n............................<br />\n裁決就有可能是死者「非法被殺」。<br />\n<br />\n陸偉雄解釋，<br />\n....................<br />\n法庭會裁定為「死於不幸」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不能直接套用民事索償<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：差人否認截停 受傷司機斥狡辯<br />\n<br />\n至於「非法被殺」裁決，陸指門檻非常高，一經裁定，律政司便可能要從刑事方向審視案件。<br />\n<br />\n近年例子有65歲的士司機陳輝旺事件，警方調查陳與乘客糾紛，陳被帶上警車時遭警員箍頸扯高，雙腳凌空，及後證實頸椎移位，一個月後不治。前年陪審團裁定陳非法被殺。<br />\n<br />\n傷亡案件經常引起民事索償，陸偉雄指死因庭的裁斷不能直接套用於民事索償，一切需要重新舉證。不過死因庭裁決往往能啟發申索人，提示打官司的方向，可根據證據考慮控告誰人，而重新舉證不困難。<br />\n<br />\n陸指本案如要向警方索償，<br